Gets the available metrics for Analysis Server

metricSpecifications.name: qpu_metric
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: QPU. Range 0-100 for S1, 0-200 for S2 and 0-400 for S4

metricSpecifications.name: memory_metric
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Memory. Range 0-25 GB for S1, 0-50 GB for S2 and 0-100 GB for S4

metricSpecifications.name: private_bytes_metric
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Private bytes.

metricSpecifications.name: virtual_bytes_metric
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Virtual bytes.

metricSpecifications.name: TotalConnectionRequests
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Total connection requests. These are arrivals.

metricSpecifications.name: SuccessfullConnectionsPerSec
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Rate of successful connection completions.

metricSpecifications.name: TotalConnectionFailures
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Total failed connection attempts.

metricSpecifications.name: CurrentUserSessions
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Current number of user sessions established.

metricSpecifications.name: QueryPoolBusyThreads
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of busy threads in the query thread pool.

metricSpecifications.name: CommandPoolJobQueueLength
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of jobs in the queue of the command thread pool.

metricSpecifications.name: ProcessingPoolJobQueueLength
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of non-I/O jobs in the queue of the processing thread pool.

metricSpecifications.name: CurrentConnections
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Current number of client connections established.

metricSpecifications.name: CleanerCurrentPrice
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Current price of memory, $/byte/time, normalized to 1000.

metricSpecifications.name: CleanerMemoryShrinkable
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Amount of memory, in bytes, subject to purging by the background cleaner.

metricSpecifications.name: CleanerMemoryNonshrinkable
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Amount of memory, in bytes, not subject to purging by the background cleaner.

metricSpecifications.name: MemoryUsage
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Memory usage of the server process as used in calculating cleaner memory price. Equal to counter Process\PrivateBytes plus the size of memory-mapped data, ignoring any memory which was mapped or allocated by the xVelocity in-memory analytics engine (VertiPaq) in excess of the xVelocity engine Memory Limit.

metricSpecifications.name: MemoryLimitHard
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Hard memory limit, from configuration file.

metricSpecifications.name: MemoryLimitHigh
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: High memory limit, from configuration file.

metricSpecifications.name: MemoryLimitLow
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Low memory limit, from configuration file.

metricSpecifications.name: MemoryLimitVertiPaq
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: In-memory limit, from configuration file.

metricSpecifications.name: Quota
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Current memory quota, in bytes. Memory quota is also known as a memory grant or memory reservation.

metricSpecifications.name: QuotaBlocked
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Current number of quota requests that are blocked until other memory quotas are freed.

metricSpecifications.name: VertiPaqNonpaged
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Bytes of memory locked in the working set for use by the in-memory engine.

metricSpecifications.name: VertiPaqPaged
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Bytes of paged memory in use for in-memory data.

metricSpecifications.name: RowsReadPerSec
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Rate of rows read from all relational databases.

metricSpecifications.name: RowsConvertedPerSec
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Rate of rows converted during processing.

metricSpecifications.name: RowsWrittenPerSec
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Rate of rows written during processing.

metricSpecifications.name: CommandPoolBusyThreads
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of busy threads in the command thread pool.

metricSpecifications.name: CommandPoolIdleThreads
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of idle threads in the command thread pool.

metricSpecifications.name: LongParsingBusyThreads
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of busy threads in the long parsing thread pool.

metricSpecifications.name: LongParsingIdleThreads
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of idle threads in the long parsing thread pool.

metricSpecifications.name: LongParsingJobQueueLength
metricSpecifications.displayName: Threads: Long parsing job queue length
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of jobs in the queue of the long parsing thread pool.

metricSpecifications.name: ProcessingPoolBusyIOJobThreads
metricSpecifications.displayName: Threads: Processing pool busy I/O job threads
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of threads running I/O jobs in the processing thread pool.

metricSpecifications.name: ProcessingPoolBusyNonIOThreads
metricSpecifications.displayName: Threads: Processing pool busy non-I/O threads
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of threads running non-I/O jobs in the processing thread pool.

metricSpecifications.name: ProcessingPoolIOJobQueueLength
metricSpecifications.displayName: Threads: Processing pool I/O job queue length
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of I/O jobs in the queue of the processing thread pool.

metricSpecifications.name: ProcessingPoolIdleIOJobThreads
metricSpecifications.displayName: Threads: Processing pool idle I/O job threads
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of idle threads for I/O jobs in the processing thread pool.

metricSpecifications.name: ProcessingPoolIdleNonIOThreads
metricSpecifications.displayName: Threads: Processing pool idle non-I/O threads
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of idle threads in the processing thread pool dedicated to non-I/O jobs.

metricSpecifications.name: QueryPoolIdleThreads
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of idle threads for I/O jobs in the processing thread pool.

metricSpecifications.name: QueryPoolJobQueueLength
metricSpecifications.displayName: Threads: Query pool job queue lengt
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of jobs in the queue of the query thread pool.

metricSpecifications.name: ShortParsingBusyThreads
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of busy threads in the short parsing thread pool.

metricSpecifications.name: ShortParsingIdleThreads
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of idle threads in the short parsing thread pool.

metricSpecifications.name: ShortParsingJobQueueLength
metricSpecifications.displayName: Threads: Short parsing job queue length
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Number of jobs in the queue of the short parsing thread pool.

metricSpecifications.name: memory_thrashing_metric
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Average memory thrashing.

metricSpecifications.name: mashup_engine_qpu_metric
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: QPU usage by mashup engine processes

metricSpecifications.name: mashup_engine_memory_metric
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Memory usage by mashup engine processes

metricSpecifications.name: mashup_engine_private_bytes_metric
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Private bytes usage by mashup engine processes.

metricSpecifications.name: mashup_engine_virtual_bytes_metric
metricSpecifications.displayDescription: Virtual bytes usage by mashup engine processes.
